	},
	{
		title: 'Software',
		body: 'I like building software that feels sharp: simple architecture, strong UX, and fast feedback.',
	},
	{
		title: 'Masters',
		body: 'Formal training helped, but I mostly learned by building, shipping, and measuring.',
	},
	{
		title: 'Human-AI collaboration',
		body: 'I care about collaboration: humans set direction and taste; AI provides leverage and speed.',
	},
	{
		title: 'Startups',
		body: 'Startups are my lab: constraints, iteration, and learning under time pressure.',
